data.description: Move-in Ready! 4 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom home offers 1,948 SQFT on an oversized .30 acre lot. Energy efficient. Everyone will want to explore this well kept and stylish home. These types of homes don't come on the market often! No rear neighbors. Features include high ceilings, spacious bedrooms, and a separate laundry room. Vaulted ceiling in great room. Make your way inside where you’ll find a spacious living room with more than enough room for a cozy living room suite and big-screen TV. Kitchen is open with breakfast bar overlooking living room. This cook's kitchen has an abundance of  36” upgraded cabinets with crown molding, featuring Stainless Steel GE appliances including Dishwasher, Range Oven and Microwave. The Dining Room is perfect for entertaining guests and family. Large laundry room with pantry. There's plenty of natural light throughout this open floor plan with split bedroom design. Heading into the primary suite, you will find plenty of closet space, and an en-suite bathroom with dual sink 36” high vanity. The additional bedrooms share a hall bathroom featuring a bathtub/shower combo. The large attached garage provides room for two cars and plenty of additional storage. Sitting close enough to many local amenities, yet away from all the commercial hustle and bustle, find this endearing home within a small neighborhood. Easy access to major roads, shopping, restaurants, and medical while still maintaining that rural Central Florida Lifestyle. Schedule Your Tour Today!
